*camsource-0.7.1 (04 Apr 2007)

  04 Apr 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  +files/camsource-0.7.1-example.patch, +files/camsource.initd,
  +camsource-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Version bump to unofficial release since upstream CVS has been quiet for
  three years. Thanks to Conrad Kostecki in bug 170349.

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  10 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add missing email address for herd with name != alias.

